It is as though Yahweh held a cup in his hand;\q2 it is filled with wine that has spices mixed in it to cause those who drink it to become more drunk;
\q1 and when Yahweh pours it out, he will force all the wicked people to drink it;
\q2 they will drink every drop of it; yes, he will punish them fully.



